original_title: The Doctors: The Tom Baker Years
overview: This is the definitive set of interviews with the team of actors who brought the TOM BAKER era of DOCTOR WHO to life!  This documentary includes the best in-depth interviews with TOM BAKER (the Fourth Doctor), ELISABETH SLADEN (Sarah Jane), IAN MARTER (Harry), LOUISE JAMESON (Leela), MARY TAMM (Romana) and JOHN LEESON (Voice of K9)!
